    <h2>Build a game (start here)</h2>
    <p>Two complete, build-along multiplayer games that use the whole SpawnWeaver toolkit —
        matchmaking, state sync, realtime events, snapshots, damage and respawns:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-2d-shooter">2D arena shooter</a> — top-down free-for-all with bullets, health, and a scoreboard.</li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-3d-shooter">3D arena shooter</a> — third-person hitscan arena, scene built entirely in code.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Feature guides</h2>
    <p>Shorter, focused guides for one feature at a time:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/sync-nodes">Drop-in sync nodes &amp; interpolation</a> — replicate movement with zero boilerplate.</li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-online">Online in 10 minutes</a> — connect, authenticate, send your first event.</li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-lobby">Build a lobby with a ready check</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-matchmaking">Add matchmaking</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-state-sync">Simple state sync</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-profile">Save a player profile</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dashboard/docs/tutorial-debug">Debug a failed connection</a></li>
    </ul>

